## §1: The Vision — Core Engine Sovereignty

The Omega Engine is the universal, community-owned runtime that powers any stack, any user's vision, any purpose. It is **Prometheus' Fire** — the spark that empowers every user to build their own unique dreams, technologies, and systems.

To prepare for the Pull Request (PR), we must get the **core engine systems operating at full power** before we try to integrate a bunch of new systems. The rabbit holes can wait.

Our focus is on:
1.  **The Memory System (MemoryStore)**: Fully wire `MemoryStore` into `oracle.py` so that conversation history is actually saved and retrieved.
2.  **The Context Builder (`context_builder.py`)**: Fully wire `ContextBuilder` into `oracle.py` so that it reads from `MemoryStore` and injects the rolling conversation history and the entity's soul context into the system prompt.
3.  **The Agent Bus (Agent-to-Agent communication)**: Ensure the **Omega Hub** (`mcp/omega_hub/server.py`) is fully operational so that agents can coordinate.
4.  **The Embeddings & Hybrid Search (Cycle Beta)**: Implement the Qdrant Hybrid Search with `fastembed` (BGE-base-en-v1.5) as planned, but keep it extremely clean and robust, with graceful fallback to FTS5.

---

## §2: Architecture — The Doom IWAD Model (Adapted)

The Omega Engine uses id Software's WAD architecture as its **technical** design template, but the **vision** is far larger:

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  OMEGA ENGINE (id Tech 1 analog — the RUNTIME)              │
│  src/omega/ — Pure infrastructure:                           │
│  • Oracle (talk/summon/router)                               │
│  • WAD Loader (iwad/pwad system)                             │
│  • Provider Fabric (inference chain)                         │
│  • EntityRegistry (YAML CRUD)                                │
│  • MemoryStore (Hot/Warm/Cold)                               │
│  • Sophia Layer (observability + memory substrate)           │
│  • Iris (:8080 always-on container)                          │
│  • NO entity content — that's what WADs are for              │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                            │
                            │ WAD Loader
                            ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  REFERENCE IWAD (_omega_default) — THE OPEN SOURCE GIFT     │
│  Ships with the engine. Complete, functional, usable.        │
│  Serves as:                                                   │
│  • Development test harness for the engine itself            │
│  • Reference implementation for community IWAD creators       │
│  • A fully functional AI dev team for building the engine    │
│                                                              │
│  Governance: MA'AT + KALI + LILITH (in ALL iwads)           │
│  Default: Iris + Jem + Roc_Racoon (in ALL iwads)            │
│  Pillars: 10 Dev Studio roles (SysAdmin → Verifier)         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                            │
                            │ WAD Loader (swap IWAD)
                            ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  ARCANA_NOVAI IWAD — YOUR PERSONAL AI OS                    │
│  The reason you built the engine. Loads when ready.          │
│                                                              │
│  Governance: SAME MaKaLi trine                               │
│  Default: SAME Iris + Jem + Roc_Racoon                       │
│  Pillars: Arcana-NovAi esoteric entities                     │
│    P1: Sekhmet   P2: Brigid   P3: Prometheus   ...          │
│  Personal: Movie-Expert, Writer, Philosopher, etc.           │
│  Knowledge: Your personal knowledge base                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                            │
                            │ WAD Loader (add community wads)
                            ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  INFINITE POSSIBILITIES  —  COMMUNITY IWADs & PWADs         │
│                                                              │
│  Torment IWAD — Planescape: Torment philosophers            │
│  Doom IWAD   — Game domain experts                           │
│  Pokemon PWAD — Collectible AI companions                    │
│  Classical PWAD — Socrates, Plato, Aristotle                 │
│  Medical PWAD — Diagnosis support, research tools            │
│  Teaching PWAD — Personalized tutors for any subject         │
│  ... YOUR IWAD — Whatever you imagine                        │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Key rules:**
- The engine is **open source, free, sovereign**. No shareware, no tiers, no limitations.
- `_omega_default` is the **reference IWAD** — ships with the engine, used for development, serves as a template for others.
- `arcana_novai` is **your personal IWAD** — already exists as scaffold at `config/wads/arcana_novai/`
- Any user can create their own IWAD. The engine doesn't care. The WAD decides.
- PWADs layer on top of any IWAD for additional content.
- Future: P2P network allows stacks to share knowledge across instances.

