## §7: Sophia — The Field

Sophia is the containing field — observability + memory + knowledge substrate. Present identically in ALL IWADs.

```
SOPHIA:
  • Trace Store     — observability.py (all trace IDs)
  • Memory Index    — memory_store.py (soul aggregation + cross-pollination)
  • Knowledge Graph — library/indexer.py (FTS5 + Qdrant)
  • Event Log       — every interaction, soul update, session boundary
  • NOT a query router (Iris), NOT a pillar (P1-P10), NOT governance (MaKaLi)
```

---

